Python library for working with Growl Notification Transport Protocol (GNTP)

client.py
Test client for showing the basic options

gntp.py
Main GNTP classes

gntp_notifier.py
Class that is supposed to be a drop in replacement for the python
bindings that come with the Growl SDK
http://code.google.com/p/growl/source/browse/Bindings/python/Growl.py

server.py
Server that listens for GNTP messages.

gntp_bridge.py
Used with server.py to 'regrowl' messages to the local Mac Growl library